casebody.data:
Thursday, February 12, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

98-68. State ex rel. Nix v. Cleveland.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of respondents’ motion to quash and for protective order,

IT IS ORDERED by the court th.at the motion to quash and for protective order be, and hereby is, denied as moot.
